_source.body:
I saw this coming a mile away.

BlackRock owns the US Treasury, and Ukraine, as well as the weapons manufacturers and reconstruction companies.

Eric Van Nostrand, BlackRock's former managing director is senior advisor on economic issues for Ukraine and Russia to the current WH.

They already bought out the infrastructure in Ukraine during the credit default swap months ago.
In fact, this agreement is really only for the sake of paper. Nearly a year ago they formed a pro-bono "advisory board" to direct Zelenskyy.

Money laundering.
Massive scale.

https://www.cnbc.com/2022/12/28/zelenskyy-blackrock-ceo-fink-agree-to-coordinate-ukraine-investment.html
